{"tid":555944,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟啲呀媽拎住條橡筋帶，綁住自己個仔喺咩心態？","createTime":"2018-02-10T04:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T10:41:04.000Z","uid":54929,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf0928a335f26482a873be8740dc35edb295ceb","tid":555944,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"喺條街見到個呀媽拎住條帶，綁住自己個仔隻手。<br />\n俗啲講句，真係成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個仔成為眾人目光，壓力一定好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0858f4145a37e6e72b346c39608a3d5e84242559","tid":555944,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c2f39a468565e2136256070f6072e5a9c7a77f4","tid":555944,"uid":47250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:17:55.000Z","msg":"驚佢仆街"},{"pid":"9b1e650a58e721d3140fe1eb4722b87c8f24fdc9","tid":555944,"uid":39698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:18:28.000Z","msg":"放狗"},{"pid":"af0c5077599a2bbe14dc2697b0d87324a1b6412b","tid":555944,"uid":54929,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放狗</blockquote><br />\n比同學仔見到會指住嚟笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34c6524c27eae5cb5e3b9cdf8ed4b963964b1b8","tid":555944,"uid":9726,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:29:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39ea5b45ca2f71eff13adb49ca79e657df33c556","tid":555944,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放狗唔用狗帶犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0ad723ed239fa1cad1b2d75694995294ed86d2","tid":555944,"uid":87511,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"通常係支那狗先用<br />\n<br />\n有一款仲要條帶係通咗少少電<br />\n好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我有次企定定，隔離隻支那仔跑過嚟但係條帶掂到我，我成個人彈一彈起<br />\n啲支那狗真係好撚濕鳩"},{"pid":"f3d18773fdf6038fd70b69dc43a521cfb97f70f9","tid":555944,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T05:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"155499facf2652817cddf79e05bf8ebe889da038","tid":555944,"uid":18366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d10c7e9cfb9df80ea97b523fe303d7a5d0e8936c","tid":555944,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:39:28.000Z","msg":"當蟲係狗算係咁啦"},{"pid":"0b70407a3d5753c7e42cf2a288b20c0802392c2e","tid":555944,"uid":86893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"盡責<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d91b7e142ba42bf389e020f3861d796bba4da5","tid":555944,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"連自己都當個仔係隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係唔怪得啲人叫佢哋做支那狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0891d6d37cc9b395bd9cde097f90ad28d759c2","tid":555944,"uid":68236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"支那多拐子佬嘛，唔綁實啲可能一出門口就唔見咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1960c279ce23845e0b3f904659217e38d7eed5","tid":555944,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dis